---
import { IDS } from "../../data/site";
---

<section id={IDS.whyJoin} class="py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Why Join Cub Scouts?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
        Scouting is more than a weekly meeting — it’s an experience that lasts a lifetime. At Pack 151, your child will:
      </p>
    </div>

    <ul class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <li class="card bg-base-200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Get Outdoors</h3>
          <p>Hike every month, camp under the stars, and explore nature.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card bg-base-200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Earn Achievements</h3>
          <p>Recognize effort, progress, and personal growth.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card bg-base-200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Make Friends</h3>
          <p>Build strong friendships across grades and schools.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card bg-base-200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Try New Things</h3>
          <p>STEM, crafts, service projects, games, and skits.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card bg-base-200 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Grow Together</h3>
          <p>Families are part of the fun, every step of the way.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-8 text-lg">
      Scouting teaches lessons that sports and school alone can’t: resilience, kindness, responsibility, and service.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>